params.1319:
Zulrah is a snake boss found at their shrine within the Poison Wastes south of Isafdar. The followers of Zul-Andra provide access to the shrine via rowboat.

Attack Styles - Melee, Ranged, Magic.
Immunities - Poison, Venom
Slayer categories - None
